mapper.sql:
with "給付実績" AS ( SELECT * FROM rgdb."DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon" AS "mst" WHERE "mst"."hiHokenshaNo" = #{被保険者番号} AND #{サービス提供年月_開始} <= "mst"."serviceTeikyoYM" AND "mst"."serviceTeikyoYM" <= #{サービス提供年月_終了}
AND "mst"."inputShikibetsuNo" not in ('71P1','8161')
AND "mst"."inputShikibetsuNo" in ('71P1','8161')
AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT 'X' FROM rgdb."DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon" AS "slv" WHERE "mst"."inputShikibetsuNo" = "slv"."inputShikibetsuNo" AND "mst"."hiHokenshaNo" = "slv"."hiHokenshaNo" AND "mst"."serviceTeikyoYM" = "slv"."serviceTeikyoYM" AND "mst"."jigyoshoNo" = "slv"."jigyoshoNo" AND "mst"."seiriNo" = "slv"."seiriNo" AND (("mst"."shinsaYM" < "slv"."shinsaYM") or ("mst"."shinsaYM" = "slv"."shinsaYM" and "slv"."kyufuSakuseiKubunCode" < "mst"."kyufuSakuseiKubunCode"))) )

mapper.select:
with "給付実績基本" AS ( SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM rgdb."DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon" AS "mst" WHERE "mst"."hiHokenshaNo" = #{被保険者番号} AND #{サービス提供年月_開始} <= "mst"."serviceTeikyoYM" AND "mst"."serviceTeikyoYM" <= #{サービス提供年月_終了} AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 'X'FROM rgdb."DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon" AS "slv" WHERE "mst"."inputShikibetsuNo" = "slv"."inputShikibetsuNo" AND "mst"."hiHokenshaNo" = "slv"."hiHokenshaNo" AND "mst"."serviceTeikyoYM" = "slv"."serviceTeikyoYM" AND "mst"."jigyoshoNo" = "slv"."jigyoshoNo" AND "mst"."seiriNo" = "slv"."seiriNo" AND (("mst"."shinsaYM" < "slv"."shinsaYM") OR ("mst"."shinsaYM" = "slv"."shinsaYM" AND "slv"."kyufuSakuseiKubunCode" < "mst"."kyufuSakuseiKubunCode")) )) as "基本"
WHERE substr("基本"."inputShikibetsuNo" ,1,3)in ('21B','812')
WHERE substr("基本"."inputShikibetsuNo",1,3) in('816')
WHERE EXISTS (select 'x' from rgdb."DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei" as "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei" WHERE "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."hiHokenshaNo" = "基本"."hiHokenshaNo" AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."serviceTeikyoYM" = "基本"."serviceTeikyoYM" AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."inputShikibetsuNo" = "基本"."inputShikibetsuNo" AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."jigyoshoNo" = "基本"."jigyoshoNo" AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."toshiNo" = "基本"."toshiNo" AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."serviceSyuruiCode" in
#{サービス種類コード}
)
WHERE substr("基本"."inputShikibetsuNo",1,3) not in ('71R','817','71P','816','21B','812')
WHERE substr("基本"."inputShikibetsuNo",1,3) in ('71R','817')
WHERE substr("基本"."inputShikibetsuNo",1,3) in ('71P')
)
